cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques for sentiment analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses neural networks, which are commonly used in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves transfer learning, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper uses attention-based LSTM, which is a type of recurrent neural network, making cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) another possible category.
